Ley Line Walker
The Ley Line Walker is a sorcerer attuned to the magical ley lines that
crisscross Rifts Earth, channelling their power into spells and dimensional
rifting. One of the most powerful magic-using OCCs in the game.

Ley Line Walkers begin with high PPE (magic energy) and a broad skill base
in languages, lore, and technical areas. They choose from Technical, Science,
Lore, and Physical categories.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12, ME 14.
PPE: Starting PPE pool (base PPE + ME) fuels spell casting.
Starting equipment: Traveller's robes or armoured jacket, spellbook, arcane
focus crystal, concealed sidearm, and starting PPE pool.
